  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil half a kettle</p><p>Pat your <strong>pork belly </strong>dry with kitchen paper, then<strong> </strong>score the<strong> fatty side</strong>, horizontally<strong> </strong>in lines, approx. an inch thick by drawing a sharp knife through the skin, deep enough to reach the meat below</p><p>Cut the <strong>scored pork</strong> in half, lengthways</p><p>Season with<strong> </strong>a very generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and rub it deep into the fat</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1702992253735-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1702992253735-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1702992253735-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1702992253735-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1702992253735-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>pork belly</strong>, fat-side down and cook for 4 min or until golden and crispy, then flip and cook for 2 min on the other side</p><p>Once done, transfer the pork to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (reserve the pan!) and put the tray in the oven for 30-35 min or until cooked through – this is your<strong> pork chicharron</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1702992256963-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1702992256963-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
