      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> with the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>aji verde</strong></p>",
